## Required UI states (every screen/component)
- **Loading** — show a loading indicator while data is in flight.
- **Error** — usable error state, not blank/crash.
- **Empty** — distinct from loading ("no items yet").
- **Success** — the normal render.

## Accessibility (non-negotiable)
- Semantic HTML (`<button>`, `<nav>`, headings in order).
- Labels for inputs; alt text for meaningful images.
- Keyboard operable; visible focus.
- Color contrast meets WCAG AA.

